íŸ@f08eaa5bfe239c4fe535898190c29d20afdfaa20b8aa8d52472864e1e091d931⁄Title: title: to msgpackz
Path: Flags
Content:
``--quality, -q {int}``
: Quality of brotli compression (default 3).
``--window-size, -w {int}``
: Window size for brotli compression (default 20).
``--serialize, -s``
: Serialize nushell types that cannot be deserialized.
